Business Requirement:-

Objective: The primary objective of the Amazon Sales Analysis Report is to provide comprehensive insights into the sales performance of products listed on Amazon. 
           This report aims to help stakeholders understand sales trends, identify top-performing products, and make data-driven decisions to optimize sales strategies and improve overall business performance.

Scope: The report will cover the following key areas:

Sales Performance: Analysis of total sales, revenue, and growth trends over specified periods.
Product Analysis: Identification of top-selling products, categories, and their contribution to overall sales.
Customer Insights: Analysis of customer demographics, purchasing behavior, and feedback.
Market Trends: Examination of market trends and their impact on sales.
Competitor Analysis: Comparison of sales performance with key competitors.

Deliverables:
A detailed Power BI report (.pbix file) with interactive dashboards and visualizations.
Monthly and quarterly sales performance summaries.
Insights and recommendations for improving sales strategies.
